        </div>

        <div class="container py-4">
            <div class="row gy-4">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div>
                        <a class="more-link-item">iPhone Phones - iPhone 15 Pro Max</a>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <a class="more-link-item">Samsung Phones - Samsung Galaxy S 24 Ultra</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div>
                        <a class="more-link-item">Laptop Asus - Laptop HP - Laptop Dell - Laptop Acer</a>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <a class="more-link-item">Gaming Laptops - Ultrabook Laptops - High-quality Laptops</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div>
                        <a class="more-link-item">Headphones - Keyboards - Chargers - Microphones - Mice - Mouse
                            Pads</a>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <a class="more-link-item">Accessories - Apple Accessories - Affordable Accessories</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div>
                        <a class="more-link-item">Discounted Products - Best Selling - New Products</a>
                    </div>
